Reasoning: The paper discusses the technical solutions and algorithms used in Real-Time Bidding (RTB) for online display advertising, which involves information retrieval, data mining, and machine learning. Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also covers revenue optimization and ad fraud detection, which could fall under cs.CE (Computational Economics) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), respectively.
